replies.body:
{{champion:92}} 

I don't actually mind the champion's kit, I just hate riven players

Now that I think about it, I hate a lot of champions only because of their playerbases

{{champion:64}} 

 Most of Riot's golden boys would be good choices; if they can't be balanced because Riot won't let them be anything less than the best, then they should be removed. Any time Lee Sin becomes #2 in the jungle he is immediately buffed, and it is sickening. You can't have hate boners for one list of champs and real boners for another, Riot, that is the opposite of balance.

 I'd also like to remove all yordles. Also Amumu is a yordle again. Also Fizz is now a yordle. And therefore removed. Yordles suck. Though I suppose Fizz is the worst of them all.
